<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="es">

<head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/estilos.css">

    <script
            src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"
            integrity="sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4="
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>


    <title>Patitas, Home</title>
</head>

<body>
{{>navbar.hbs}}
<div class="container mt-4 justify-content-center table-bordered rounded bg-secondary shadow-lg border-radius">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col d-flex justify-content-center">
            <h1 class="pt-4 mb-4">Contacto</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col d-flex justify-content-center">
            <h5>Completa la informacion de cada contacto de emergencia.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col d-flex justify-content-center">
        <h5>Este se va a utilizar si alguien encuentra tu mascota y lo quiere reportar.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <form class="col-3"></form>

        <form class="col-6 m-4" action="/agregar-contacto/{{persona.id}}" method="post">

            <div class="form-group row my-1">
                <div class="col-2">
                    <label for="text" class="col-form-label">Nombre</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="input-group">

                        <input id="text" name="inputNombre" type="text" required="required" class="form-control rounded" pattern="[A-Za-z]+">

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group row my-1">
                <div class="col-2">
                    <label for="text" class="col-form-label">Apellido</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input id="text" name="inputApellido" type="text" required="required" class="form-control rounded" pattern="[A-Za-z]+">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group row my-1">
                <div class="col-2">
                    <label for="text" class="col-form-label">Email</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input id="text" name="inputEmail" type="email" required="required" class="form-control rounded">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group row my-1">
                <div class="col-2">
                    <label for="text" class="col-form-label">Telefono</label>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input id="text" name="inputTelefono" type="tel" required="required" class="form-control rounded">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group row">
                <div class="col d-flex justify-content-around">
                    <button name="submit" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary px-5 my-4 rounded-pill">Guardar este contacto.</button>
                    <a href=../><button name="returnHome" type="button" class="btn btn-primary px-5 my-4 rounded-pill">Volver al Home</button></a>

                </div>
            </div>
        </form>

        <form class="col-3 m-4"></form>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="libs/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>

</html>